    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/92368eb3c7e61fa2c5278e071d6f9ee9.avif?t=1727144743\" width=620 height=170 /></span><br><br>Pick up blocks from the ground and throw them around to attack enemies!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/4e5824147b6db546bb5e9b211c394f38.poster.avif?t=1727144743\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/4e5824147b6db546bb5e9b211c394f38.webm?t=1727144743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/4e5824147b6db546bb5e9b211c394f38.mp4?t=1727144743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/1b56babd29e07522748cd13bee424323.avif?t=1727144743\" width=620 height=230 /></span><br><br>While throwing blocks is your main attack resource, it also limits the space you have to walk in the island. Be careful! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/82de6ea3c16ffe82e1e9bcdda2260bc3.poster.avif?t=1727144743\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/82de6ea3c16ffe82e1e9bcdda2260bc3.webm?t=1727144743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/82de6ea3c16ffe82e1e9bcdda2260bc3.mp4?t=1727144743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/38253053703ea4b36944a2f36fbff868.avif?t=1727144743\" width=620 height=230 /></span><br><br>In each island, you will face a variety of new enemies and bosses. From silly fruit slimes to ghostly sailors, these lands hide a lot of dangerous creatures that will challenge your path.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/5bd289d9b846a1160be161a7a24842b7.poster.avif?t=1727144743\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/5bd289d9b846a1160be161a7a24842b7.webm?t=1727144743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/5bd289d9b846a1160be161a7a24842b7.mp4?t=1727144743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/834b7d3ca36b85d8fb60c98498b6a1eb.avif?t=1727144743\" width=620 height=230 /></span><br><br>Unlock new items as you progress your adventure and explore new combinations. Customize your cat with different hats, gloves and accessories to create never seen before synergies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/2e86aaa4615ec517f1412298e479188c.poster.avif?t=1727144743\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/2e86aaa4615ec517f1412298e479188c.webm?t=1727144743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148480/extras/2e86aaa4615ec517f1412298e479188c.mp4?t=1727144743\" type=\"video